      "output": "<path>C:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\Downloads\\Google AI Studio-20260623T104922Z-3-001_extracted\\Google AI Studio\\Discrepancy in Shower Rail Inventory_</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: {\n2:   \"runSettings\": {\n3:     \"temperature\": 1.0,\n4:     \"model\": \"models/gemini-3.1-flash-lite-preview\",\n5:     \"topP\": 0.95,\n6:     \"topK\": 64,\n7:     \"maxOutputTokens\": 65536,\n8:     \"safetySettings\": [{\n9:       \"category\": \"HARM_CATEGORY_HARASSMENT\",\n10:       \"threshold\": \"OFF\"\n11:     }, {\n12:       \"category\": \"HARM_CATEGORY_HATE_SPEECH\",\n13:       \"threshold\": \"OFF\"\n14:     }, {\n15:       \"category\": \"HARM_CATEGORY_SEXUALLY_EXPLICIT\",\n16:       \"threshold\": \"OFF\"\n17:     }, {\n18:       \"category\": \"HARM_CATEGORY_DANGEROUS_CONTENT\",\n19:       \"threshold\": \"OFF\"\n20:     }],\n21:     \"enableCodeExecution\": false,\n22:     \"enableSearchAsATool\": true,\n23:     \"enableBrowseAsATool\": false,\n24:     \"enableAutoFunctionResponse\": false,\n25:     \"thinkingBudget\": -1,\n26:     \"googleSearch\": {\n27:     },\n28:     \"outputResolution\": \"1K\",\n29:     \"thinkingLevel\": \"THINKING_MINIMAL\",\n30:     \"enableImageSearch\": false,\n31:     \"enableGoogleMaps\": false\n32:   },\n33:   \"systemInstruction\": {\n34:   },\n35:   \"chunkedPrompt\": {\n36:     \"chunks\": [{\n37:       \"driveImage\": {\n38:         \"id\": \"1eEWpuUtBf4d2tWgEccn6SzwH3g6in6R1\"\n39:       },\n40:       \"role\": \"user\",\n41:       \"tokenCount\": 1065,\n42:       \"createTime\": \"2026-03-29T22:34:32.079Z\"\n43:     }, {\n44:       \"text\": \"i\\u0027ve moved into this new house in the uk and i am looking at the inventory but this has not been reported but i have been given a tenant pack with inventory and amendmenr sheet and i think this is not it for the state of this shower thing as u can see around the tube i dont know what to call it.\",\n45:       \"role\": \"user\",\n46:       \"tokenCount\": 69,\n47:       \"createTime\": \"2026-03-29T22:34:32.079Z\"\n48:     }, {\n49:       \"text\": \"It is very common to find discrepancies between a property\\u0027s actual condition and the initial inventory report. Because you are in a new tenancy, it is essential to act quickly to protect your deposit.\\n\\n### 1. Identify the item\\nThe item in the photo is a **shower curtain rail** (or rod). The area where the rod meets the wall is usually covered by a **flange** or **bracket**, which is meant to hide the mounting screws and hold the rod in place.\\n\\n### 2. Document the issue immediately\\nYou must create a \\\"paper trail\\\" to prove that this condition existed before you moved in. \\n*   **Take your own photos/videos:** Take clear, well-lit photos of the rusted area, including a few close-ups and some wider shots to show where it is located in the bathroom. Ensure your camera settings are on a date-stamp mode if possible, or keep the digital files with their original metadata (date taken).\\n*   **Create a list:** Write down a clear, objective description of the rust. You can describe it as: *\\\"Significant rust and corrosion visible on the shower curtain rail and its mounting bracket.\\\"*\\n\\n### 3. Contact your landlord or letting agent\\nYou need to inform them of this discrepancy in writing as soon as possible. Even if you have already mentioned it verbally, a written record (email is best) is vital for your protection.\\n\\n**Draft email/letter template:**\\n\\n\\u003e **Subject:** Notification of pre-existing condition – [Your Address]\\n\\u003e\\n\\u003e Dear [Landlord or Letting Agent Name],\\n\\u003e\\n\\u003e I am writing regarding the inventory report provided for [Your Address]. Upon moving in, I conducted an inspection and noted a discrepancy regarding the shower curtain rail that was not recorded in the initial inventory.\\n\\u003e\\n\\u003e Please find attached photographs of the shower curtain rail. There is significant rust and corrosion on the rail and the mounting bracket. \\n\\u003e\\n\\u003e Please could you update your records to include this as a pre-ex... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\n50:       \"role\": \"model\",\n51:       \"grounding\": {\n52:         \"corroborationSegments\": [{\n53:           \"index\": 1210,\n54:           \"uri\": \"https://www.google.com/url?sa\\u003dE\\u0026q\\u003dhttps%3A%2F%2Fvertexaisearch.cloud.google.com%2Fgrounding-api-redirect%2FAUZIYQG87ceOrx5AxT2L3dsTdwsR_364hGUcA1iR6LgYCin203odWY6nwWtwUmwOtTpA7dEM9-5mQ-w12FLv8ygexi_kvrgRhzYmMZ6yB6fTW9IMMu6H--kq4NWGpLRRdBR3eH9weFy9294%3D\",\n55:           \"footnoteNumber\": 1\n56:         }, {\n57:           \"index\": 1210,\n58:           \"uri\": \"https://www.google.com/url?sa\\u003dE\\u0026q\\u003dhttps%3A%2F%2Fvertexaisearch.cloud.google.com%2Fgrounding-api-redirect%2FAUZIYQEYFpxIhb8r5pPi7twrVAyoxeu31eSlb5jYUJFhKghlwqUB-0LZR_ZX7YZtKzSDR4hld5l2AadOsJBZUJmsev79EXS-2XGZRXQaGTK2W8pl5tNtV_AaPUCj9qbn51X5mvIUeOJPuEUzT9_MvUqKrJySFSneiX8-TquUpr0mKjAW5azhtLPWBwjWPWzhSGKL16DcfjrxZ5d48XPcADM%3D\",\n59:           \"footnoteNumber\": 2\n60:         }, {\n61:           \"index\": 1210,\n62:           \"uri\": \"https://www.google.com/url?sa\\u003dE\\u0026q\\u003dhttps%3A%2F%2Fvertexaisearch.cloud.google.com%2Fgrounding-api-redirect%2FAUZIYQH-40pXp_chft_2lL9PZZSWFlE_kOuhy5n0hZEvimPfqB3ZiaDwhxRZZDv3bnoW-DvjBoVmtfBB18lJKtC60rklFAscBqOuqKWrIKLvgPLW_cLUjWDhNVs-RQdwYOKQ9hX1SH8ikVZ49INrW7eF5MX2bCCfGCg2rbuzMu6PqoWZZ1AW6QGKZT6H5Uat1mwB1IYKjcYeDPnvZX5-zaI%3D\",\n63:           \"footnoteNumber\": 3\n64:         }, {\n65:           \"index\": 1210,\n66:           \"uri\": \"https://www.google.com/url?sa\\u003dE\\u0026q\\u003dhttps%3A%2F%2Fvertexaisearch.cloud.google.com%2Fgrounding-api-redirect%2FAUZIYQEcsaNkYxEhILofrfzJv5E1MYsq_7iTBaHp8m5B6aGYnY8o5yAeYosSHvBGIqV4erve52oE2NBAWxJPtigNzRmUmxAp1XNpk45pJKfOeFfhrisuVAFwUqV1WexII0qw0RZYGlVk_IvV3eeDbo-A9eCFqrfDZyOIs042MM1TUCTg57Y2JskMkhvRN2TuG638tIFQ\",\n67:           \"footnoteNumber\": 4\n68:         }, {\n69:           \"index\": 1210,\n70:           \"uri\": \"https://www.google.com/url?sa\\u003dE\\u0026q\\u003dhttps%3A%2F%2Fvertexaisearch.cloud.google.com%2Fgrounding-api-redirect%2FAUZIYQGT5dEdg19cCaR24YDrjkOIjdaDja_Ob-61ZaoEQR7i9wg_ivcFZXZkEdI9K94aEXuWMsLEbA2LraWc9fB9q09fNZIXIhqXVxSzwGkiEcW2k3Z7yEGZ7IKGTbNuMMG8pczP66j4z6v-jqoVBZFanKer8QKm6uzZLU_Z-JS1BEqScUOd4ZltyZ4fDsdcrA%3D%3D\",\n71:           \"footnoteNumber\": 5\n72:         }, {\n73:           \"index\": 2315,\n74:           \"uri\": \"https://www.google.com/url?sa\\u003dE\\u0026q\\u003dhttps%3A%2F%2Fvertexaisearch.cloud.google.com%2Fgrounding-api-redirect%2FAUZIYQEcsaNkYxEhILofrfzJv5E1MYsq_7iTBaHp8m5B6aGYnY8o5yAeYosSHvBGIqV4erve52oE2NBAWxJPtigNzRmUmxAp1XNpk45pJKfOeFfhrisuVAFwUqV1WexII0qw0RZYGlVk_IvV3eeDbo-A9eCFqrfDZyOIs042MM1TUCTg57Y2JskMkhvRN2TuG638tIFQ\",\n75:           \"footnoteNumber\": 4\n76:         }, {\n77:           \"index\": 2315,\n78:           \"uri\": \"https://www.google.com/url?sa\\u003dE\\u0026q\\u003dhttps%3A%2F%2Fvertexaisearch.cloud.google.com%2Fgrounding-api-redirect%2FAUZIYQGT5dEdg19cCaR24YDrjkOIjdaDja_Ob-61ZaoEQR7i9wg_ivcFZXZkEdI9K94aEXuWMsLEbA2LraWc9fB9q09fNZIXIhqXVxSzwGkiEcW2k3Z7yEGZ7IKGTbNuMMG8pczP66j4z6v-jqoVBZFanKer8QKm6uzZLU_Z-JS1BEqScUOd4ZltyZ4fDsdcrA%3D%3D\",\n79:           \"footnoteNumber\": 5\n80:         }, {\n81:           \"index\": 2315,\n82:           \"uri\": \"https://www.google.com/url?sa\\u003dE\\u0026q\\u003dhttps%3A%2F%2Fvertexaisearch.cloud.google.com%2Fgrounding-api-redirect%2FAUZIYQEfe8SUZqxpbeohpiALtR5ePF7eunu27Z9OvfandumEncgGUCVGS8b2RafUsXc-3km6AKgpZN798vky7r7hDZnC0l-3YcS58Vvrc1V26o45sHbf-nNbO8pR0VCD40aHEOi4eniGooSq7SKQo4LfySR21BXWoc62bJNjJtrujhYf63VjkZutzuRPEOfvjCSJ\",\n83:           \"footnoteNumber\": 6\n84:         }, {\n85:           \"index\": 2315,\n86:           \"uri\": \"https://www.google.com/url?sa\\u003dE\\u0026q\\u003dhttps%3A%2F%2Fvertexaisearch.cloud.google.com%2Fgrounding-api-redirect%2FAUZIYQEPSR-Eo3GUtwPah4khLqikEW98O3uHx7u3n1xQXxl