kcOPF9njEtM9Pp6Kowy2aZl-4aUaZ84U6KpACSJ__UGSaSYxaRn-3quAyL8X4XDeyHj62tBVW1U\",\n276:           \"title\": \"alpinekb.com.au\"\n277:         }, {\n278:           \"referenceNumber\": 2,\n279:           \"uri\": \"https://www.google.com/url?sa\\u003dE\\u0026q\\u003dhttps%3A%2F%2Fvertexaisearch.cloud.google.com%2Fgrounding-api-redirect%2FAUZIYQGhS-qYodpjebCqgeh7HB-9X8JBYCGJTmF6avzatACbujSNCVRy8ljf7u47c3ID_HPe_FhmkRjhRhmcyl4vZtq4xReHsnGJjrfd3VG5OopHZoVVLlgxVe4aroJHH5hjHtJ6e1SIia-CoaPlUXCi2kaMXtkm\",\n280:           \"title\": \"angi.com\"\n281:         }, {\n282:           \"referenceNumber\": 3,\n283:           \"uri\": \"https://www.google.com/url?sa\\u003dE\\u0026q\\u003dhttps%3A%2F%2Fvertexaisearch.cloud.google.com%2Fgrounding-api-redirect%2FAUZIYQHUcJFSaEWi1Y3-JP-ommkwnhbnjiarXGKIkYZQ7whKKcYU2qs6jtRPQJvFYaSaQ5QRvVVZ2zuGhlnwNVtcCv-IGMBSTmeqHoWmq5lVkFq0WDbkNxt5TOPl337C0XU-IWOC1X4MlrvHVYOdNvWrrPIJ1ZDTWgiV6ehfrUg%3D\",\n284:           \"title\": \"budgetplumbingonline.com\"\n285:         }, {\n286:           \"referenceNumber\": 4,\n287:           \"uri\": \"https://www.google.com/url?sa\\u003dE\\u0026q\\u003dhttps%3A%2F%2Fvertexaisearch.cloud.google.com%2Fgrounding-api-redirect%2FAUZIYQFwrgc3jVR6a7r2KjzAH6ZWrgDZ5PnZypNvl6e2kt2rC9GiwT6zfEgkKNiSmEd9TSVg3m5bxBysWw6BE_ZTIxaeqjkH4yXOcbQHocAizOMUFcpaW4BqoWEM9zkidFMOtbQtzD9DrI8SMHz5sRXKRM_SQoH5iAOfhzKkcCSoKjMtK56wE8c-OKd1cIFF\",\n288:           \"title\": \"plumbitonline.co.za\"\n289:         }, {\n290:           \"referenceNumber\": 5,\n291:           \"uri\": \"https://www.google.com/url?sa\\u003dE\\u0026q\\u003dhttps%3A%2F%2Fvertexaisearch.cloud.google.com%2Fgrounding-api-redirect%2FAUZIYQFK0hPudrRn8BYu3khyB2KhWRcFU2TlE2XONuMXRh59MoZcZdLpsLoPkJnUa8PVT8t5tesykjUrrWudvPCeZGHxQdtJ2lC47wtc2AfhU4YNmlvDHrrWnYaZyJ4XYEtbosmlRVKAp2jsIvHMieqoyKLG0jw03GkYvmKnKRHOCO5OJrKo-Yv8NBNpuPnlrwW0I5cMUgZ1blE%3D\",\n292:           \"title\": \"astralbathware.com\"\n293:         }, {\n294:           \"referenceNumber\": 6,\n295:           \"uri\": \"https://www.google.com/url?sa\\u003dE\\u0026q\\u003dhttps%3A%2F%2Fvertexaisearch.cloud.google.com%2Fgrounding-api-redirect%2FAUZIYQElk9_El4CV06U3nRzPENzuAsUq3LRzDujw7C1DQD1L9mMl1wFTU1WgHWqtPCNrkQprkeaVnm1LYIoop3EmDbXP7uq3hxWh0M8zy7t43czvSsFYy_HKLF5T4hVOpfHNYhqy7xFFygTMDnhh2kSBy0apyk4%3D\",\n296:           \"title\": \"abiinteriors.co.uk\"\n297:         }, {\n298:           \"referenceNumber\": 7,\n299:           \"uri\": \"https://www.google.com/url?sa\\u003dE\\u0026q\\u003dhttps%3A%2F%2Fvertexaisearch.cloud.google.com%2Fgrounding-api-redirect%2FAUZIYQEMxv3AJNgdgfEZp8o9o7MPGU1DnfTx83k1zIDC7cxT_pFk74N4bK1aawucCOCpfioo2f8rf6C0o3R4hJ4j-rRM86pryxQZ_dqO4brWbHE50ejwMJNvlvq5RIpwp3Oc8RO7U-A3LiLl2WipZm8xLeFGocilvlqUMvvl\",\n300:           \"title\": \"cobbe.com\"\n301:         }]\n302:       },\n303:       \"finishReason\": \"STOP\",\n304:       \"tokenCount\": 213,\n305:       \"parts\": [{\n306:         \"text\": \"\"\n307:       }, {\n308:         \"text\": \"That part\"\n309:       }, {\n310:         \"text\": \" is called a **shower arm**.\\n\\nIt is the pipe that connects the showerhead to the water\"\n311:       }, {\n312:         \"text\": \" supply coming out of your wall. As you can see, it includes the arm itself and the small plate against the wall (often called an\"\n313:       }, {\n314:         \"text\": \" **escutcheon** or **flange**), which is meant to cover the hole where the plumbing enters the wall.\\n\\nSince\"\n315:       }, {\n316:         \"text\": \" you are documenting this for your landlord, you can refer to it as:\\n\\n*   **\\\"The shower arm and\"\n317:       }, {\n318:         \"text\": \" its wall-mounted flange/escutcheon.\\\"**\\n\\nYou can describe the issue in your email as:\\n*\\\"There is visible\"\n319:       }, {\n320:         \"text\": \" corrosion and heavy rusting on the shower arm and the flange/escutcheon where it meets the tiled wall.\\\"*\\n\\nFollowing\"\n321:       }, {\n322:         \"text\": \" the advice in the previous response—taking clear photos and emailing them to your landlord/agent immediately—is definitely the right move\"\n323:       }, {\n324:         \"text\": \". This ensures that the poor condition of these fixtures is officially recorded as pre-existing, so you won\\u0027t be\"\n325:       }, {\n326:         \"text\": \" held responsible for the corrosion when you eventually move out.\"\n327:       }, {\n328:         \"text\": \"\",\n329:         \"thoughtSignature\": \"EjQKMgG+Pvb7WwJaXq+3fto7kwrsMBvJbIbdUzLRCIJ8TXi/kKTt0CRDPo8GymZuaFUlTAtw\"\n330:       }],\n331:       \"createTime\": \"2026-03-29T22:34:55.365Z\"\n332:     }, {\n333:       \"role\": \"user\",\n334:       \"inlineImage\": {\n335:         \"mimeType\": \"image/png\",\n336:         \"data\": \"... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\n337:       },\n338:       \"tokenCount\": 1101,\n339:       \"createTime\": \"2026-03-29T22:43:37.656Z\"\n340:     }, {\n341:       \"text\": \"i dont think this is right as well, why would thi snot be tested like u know what i mean\",\n342:       \"role\": \"user\",\n343:       \"tokenCount\": 23,\n344:       \"createTime\": \"2026-03-29T22:43:37.656Z\"\n345:     }, {\n346:       \"text\": \"You are absolutely right to be concerned about this. In the UK, safety regulations regarding smoke and carbon monoxide (CO) alarms are very strict for landlords.\\n\\n### Why \\\"Unable to Verify\\\" is a major red flag\\nUnder current UK law (The Smoke and Carbon Monoxide Alarm Regulations), **a landlord is legally required to ensure that smoke and carbon monoxide alarms are in proper working order on the day the tenancy begins.**\\n\\nWriting \\\"Unable to verify\\\" on an official document for a safety-critical item is unacceptable. It essentially means they have failed to perform their legal duty to ensure you are safe from fire and carbon monoxide poisoning before you moved in.\\n\\n### Immediate Action Plan\\n\\n**1. Do not accept this inventory**\\nDo not sign off on the inventory as it currently stands. You have the right to amend the document. You should clearly mark that item as **\\\"Not tested / Status unknown - Safety concern\\\"** and add a note that the landlord must verify it immediately.\\n\\n**2. Send a formal email immediately**\\nThis is a health and safety issue, so it takes priority over cosmetic issues like the rusty shower arm. Send an email to your letting agent or landlord today.\\n\\n**Draft Email Template:**\\n\\n\\u003e **Subject: URGENT: Safety Alarm Verification Required - [Your Address]**\\n\\u003e\\n\\u003e Dear [Landlord/Agent Name],\\n\\u003e\\n\\u003e I am writing regarding the inventory report provided for my tenancy at [Your Address].\\n\\u003e\\n\\u003e I have noted that the inventory lists the \\\"Alarm\\\" (Ref: AL1) as \\\"Unable to verify.\\\"\\n\\u003e\\n\\u003e Under the Smoke and Carbon Monoxide Alarm (England) Regulations, a landlord is legally required to ensure that prescribed alarms are in proper working order at the start of a new tenancy.\\n\\u003e\\n\\u003e As this check has not been completed, I am concerned about the safety of the property. Please arrange for a professional or a qualified person to test these alarms, confirm they are in full working orde... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\n347:       \"role\": \"model\",\n348:       \"grounding\": {\n349:         \"corroborationSegments\": [{\n350:           \"index\": 161,\n351:           \"uri\": \"https://www.google.com/url?sa\\u003dE\\u0026q\\u003dhttps%3A%2F%2Fvertexaisearch.cloud.google.com%2Fgrounding-api-redirect%2FAUZIYQHPHKP7NJoJQdf5ckIeCAztslSt4tbE-KcUzYd1X9V8xEgBZeGfVj9wBdww786lUxayJxyiv4_FyLzsr6dU7925u96FFw6f3EViWMKRkyZtTH931QiBYlMHhnfJAYAH1CyVZ3iiU8UpGtvmtm6Yzj1TVEHUyy_g0q7zMrl-jhPvLO62zuf27j72EiRZx9q5v-SC2mbhOw03K8nd1sGufpUxuIsxBg%3D%3D\",\n352:           \"footnoteNumber\": 1\n353:         }, {\n354:           \"index\": 161,\n355:           \"uri\": \"https://www.google.com/url?sa\\u003dE\\u0026q\\u003dhttps%3A%2F%2Fvertexaisea